        <p>display: flex; - div kula suruki or size small pani correct ah vachurum<br/>
        flex-wrap: wrap; -  surukama or size change panama same size la arrange pani vachurum<br/>
        justify-content: space-between; - space ah pirichu equal ah content ku share panirum<br/>
        justify-content: space-around; - suthiyum space pirichu kuduthurum<br/>
        gap: 10px; - namaku thevayana gap ah naamae kuduthukalam<br/>
        justify-content: center; - for x axis, alaga center la pirichu kuduthurum<br/>
        align-items: center; - both x axis and y axis center la align aagirum
    </p>

